follow these instructions to setup client and server
Keep in mind that client has to also install snmp packet as well as the ones suggested
Server needs to install snmp and snmp-mibs-downloader
In case of Debian not finding the packets there is one:
wget and then install(dpkg -i)
https://packages.debian.org/squeeze/all/snmp-mibs-downloader/download
